{"tid":2263984,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續公開信 我是同佳","createTime":"2020-10-30T09:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T09:34:44.000Z","uid":309192,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa53f7082ab7b9edc586ab1adefa5202d8a6bbf","tid":2263984,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"最後一雙腳　惹盡塵埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉在台灣殺害女友潘曉穎的疑犯陳同佳，因洗黑錢罪在港服刑，去年10月23日刑滿出獄至今快一年，惟他赴台投案的計劃陷入僵局，且引起香港及台灣當局的爭論。潘曉穎的母親今日（20日）親到政府總部，再向保安局長李家超遞交公開信，她讀信期間更哭起來。她亦在信中設回條，讓李家超圈出「會」或「不會」馬上與台方刑偵人員交換案件資料，以便陳同佳在10月23日出獄滿一年前，對準台方窗口辦理及啟程赴台投案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201020/s00001/1603183953116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00001%2F1603183953116&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=8a7c4834\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00001%2F1603183953116&h=43c61751\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201020/s00001/1603183953116</a>"}]}